---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="页面未找到｜Uronika" description="请求的页面不存在。" noindex>
  <section class="not-found section-shell">
    <p class="eyebrow">404 / Not Found</p>
    <h1>这件作品还不在这里。</h1>
    <p>链接可能已经变化，或者内容仍在准备中。你可以回到首页，或继续浏览作品库。</p>
    <div>
      <a class="button button--primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
      <a class="button button--secondary" href="/works/">浏览作品</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .not-found {
    display: grid;
    align-content: center;
    min-height: 100svh;
    padding-block: 130px;
  }

  .not-found h1 {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 9vw, 8rem);
  }

  .not-found > p:not(.eyebrow) {
    max-width: 620px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .not-found > div {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
</style>

